Every Hero Has an Origin Story

About SOAR Conference

Our Mission

SOAR empowers healthcare leaders to discover and develop their unique superpowers, fostering innovation and excellence in patient care.

Our Vision

To create a league of extraordinary healthcare professionals who transform their organizations and communities through heroic leadership.

Our Values

Courage, Innovation, Collaboration, Excellence, and Compassion - the core powers that drive superhero healthcare leaders.
